name: Gemini Ablation
desc:
During the Main Phase: You can discard 1 card, then activate 1 of these effects.
● Special Summon 1 Gemini monster from your Deck. It becomes an Effect Monster and gains its effect.
● Tribute 1 Gemini monster, and if you do, Special Summon 1 FIRE Warrior monster from your hand or Deck. Then if you Tributed a Gemini monster that gained its effect, you can destroy 1 card on the field.
You can only use this effect of "Gemini Ablation" once per turn.
str2: Special Summon 1 Gemini monster from your Deck
str3: Tribute 1 Gemini monster, and if you do, Special Summon 1 FIRE Warrior monster from your hand or Deck
